<topic id='business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__standard_.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: NHS Continuing Healthcare (Standard) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__standard_">NHS Continuing Healthcare (Standard)</xref>
 is a type of 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__standard_">NHS Continuing Healthcare (Standard)</xref>
 is 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>
 that is not 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__fast_track_">Fast Track</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__standard_">NHS Continuing Healthcare (Standard)</xref>
:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
Includes cases that have been agreed eligible via the standard 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>
 assessment route and those 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__fast_track_">Fast Track</xref>
 cases that have been reviewed and changed to 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__standard_">Standard NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>
            </p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
Does not include 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare_previously_unassessed_period_of_care">Previously Unassessed Periods of Care</xref>
 (
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare_previously_unassessed_period_of_care">PUPoC</xref>
s).        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
For further information on 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__standard_">NHS Continuing Healthcare (Standard)</xref>
, see the:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_department_of_health_and_social_care">Department of Health and Social Care</xref>
            <p>
 part of the gov.uk website at: 
                <xref href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/national-framework-for-nhs-continuing-healthcare-and-nhs-funded-nursing-care"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">National framework for NHS continuing healthcare and NHS-funded nursing care</xref>
            </p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
            <p>
 website at: 
                <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/healthcare/"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>
.        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>

